Subject: 3D Printing and the Tabletop Game Industry
Description: 3D Printing will change many different industries and tabletop gaming will be one of the first.  Using the copyright wars of the past 15 years as a model, we'll look at the challenges 3D printing creates for tabletop game creators and explore ways companies can embrace the technology without being hostile to their customers.Jason is the creator of tabletop game Legends of Kalidasia.  Speakers include:Jason Rutherford
